text: Nice place for athletes. The cycling track is awesome, place is clean and toilet is big for everyone to use
My exercise jogging stadium. I dropped by the stadium at least twice a week. I love to run at the stadium 🏃‍♀️ Be it rain 🌧 or shine ⛅️ I am still running here ✌🏻

Very nice facilities!
The gym is deceptively big
Has a nice swimming complex on level 2

Level 2 has mirrors open for all to use, but the area is very warm with no air circulation

I am a Taekwon-Do coach at this stadium, conducting my lessons in the Level 5 studio. I enjoy the great view every time before I start the lesson, facing the pool and witnessing the many activities happening in the stadium, making it a happening place for families. My class is every Tuesday from 5:30 to 6:30 pm on Level 5. I am a happy coach to have lessons here. 😊👍🌟Chang TaeKwon-Do Singapore 🇸🇬 81204311
Good run, quite big wit cycling and roller skate track
